title: Somehow Wit Da Spring (2016)
overview: Marko and Nedeljko, best friends since high school аnd now in their early twenties, are seriously starting to think that Stefana and Nemanja, the most popular high school sweethearts, are possessed by aliens. They decide to investigate, which is unfortunate since they are heavily intoxicated with alcohol and drugs.
storyline: Two high school friends and potheads, Marko and Nedeljko, now in their early twenties, are beginning to think that the former high school jock, Stefan and his fiancée, Nevena, have aliens invaded their bodies. Marko and Nedeljko begin to follow their every step and the chaos slowly ensues.
